snippet.title: Kabuto Park - Trailer 🪲☀️🦋
snippet.description:
Enjoy summer in Kabuto Park! Capture the cutest bugs, train them and win the Summer Beetle Battles Championship in this little bug collection game! Upgrade your equipment to find rarer, stronger and shinier beetles, butterflies, bees or dragonflies.

Wishlist now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3376990/Kabuto_Park/

Join the discord to become a playtester!
https://discord.gg/aqy3uAXVDj
